{"root":{"data":{"id":"dhr36rl2z2o0","created":1775987955823,"text":"Resilient Manufacturing-韧性制造","font-weight":"bold"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr384v2cv40","created":1775988063089,"text":"概念和重要性","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr3fypnqcg0","created":1775988676614,"text":"Resilience 系统在扰动后恢复稳定的动态能力\nResiliency 系统表现韧性的静态状态属性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhr3h0fo6hs0","created":1775988758728,"text":"Resilient Manufacturing 系统在运行过程中保持业务连续性的能力 ","layout_right_offset":{"x":21,"y":0},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr4f49csew0","created":1775991431435,"text":"静态韧性-无中断，维持运行稳定性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhr4f7ar4540","created":1775991438050,"text":"动态韧性-中断下，感知预测学习适应的循环过程"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhr4gpakcxc0","created":1775991555585,"text":"三大驱动力：社会经济驱动，技术创新驱动，环境保护驱动"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhr389osij40","created":1775988073593,"text":"识别扰动","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr4r86mw280","created":1775992380348,"text":"扰动-通过制造不连续性、混乱或失序来中断或阻碍正常运营的事件"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr4s5qd5z40","created":1775992453374,"text":"外部扰动：自然灾害，疫情"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhr4sceimv40","created":1775992467896,"text":"内部扰动：设备故障，技术失误"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhr4slulh600","created":1775992488459,"text":"五级分类框架&预防与响应策略"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr4spjcmog0","created":1775992496486,"text":"机器级"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr4vvtan7c0","created":1775992745240,"text":"预测性维护"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhr4ssfmvxs0","created":1775992502792,"text":"操作级"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr4vyujmio0","created":1775992751846,"text":"协同计划"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhr4suboi7k0","created":1775992506906,"text":"企业级"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhr4svwob7k0","created":1775992510352,"text":"市场与社会级"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhr4v67h6a00","created":1775992689502,"text":"扰动的演化模式"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr4veovt080","created":1775992707968,"text":"正常"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr4vhfikww0","created":1775992713932,"text":"异常"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr4vkmhtew0","created":1775992720885,"text":"灾难"},"children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhr38e9r21s0","created":1775988083569,"text":"韧性评估","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr51qmh9t40","created":1775993204129,"text":"定性对比"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr51zzeqfs0","created":1775993224502,"text":"鲁棒性：鲁棒性侧重于在不发生中断的情况下维持实时稳定性，而韧性则强调中断后的快速适应与恢复"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhr52cj26o00","created":1775993251812,"text":"脆弱性：脆弱性关注系统内在的弱点，而韧性强调组织抵抗外部威胁并进行调整的能力"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhr52dud79k0","created":1775993254672,"text":"可靠性：可靠性要求在特定时间内不发生性能下降，而韧性允许短暂的性能损失以实现最终的“反弹”"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhr52eyzbvk0","created":1775993257128,"text":"可持续性：可持续性关注资源供应的长期平衡，韧性则侧重于丢失功能的再生"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhr532futeo0","created":1775993308214,"text":"核心维度"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr536qahig0","created":1775993317553,"text":"Absorbency 吸收力：第一道防线，指系统以最小努力吸收扰动冲击并使后果最小化的能力，通常与系统冗余度和鲁棒性相关"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhr53m9b0mg0","created":1775993351354,"text":"Adaptability 适应力：第二道防线，指系统在扰动超过吸收极限时，通过临时或非常规措施进行调整以防止行为不连续的能力"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhr53ta9dmw0","created":1775993366649,"text":"Recoverability 恢复力：第三道防线，也是韧性的核心，指系统在中断后高效反弹至预期性能水平的能力"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhr38y0njoo0","created":1775988126553,"text":"韧性增强","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr5hj8mpb40","created":1775994441881,"text":"系统设计"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr5j34n8080","created":1775994563540,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhr5hol9d280","created":1775994453529,"text":"系统配置"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhr5hpoeqkg0","created":1775994455896,"text":"系统运行"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhr39lcpja80","created":1775988177348,"text":"实现韧性的挑战","layout":null},"children":[]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}